{{Databox|ar=أبو منجل ناسك}}'''Adanay armiti''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|Taserɣint]] : أبو منجل الأصلع ) iga yan wanaw n [[Agḍiḍ|waylaln]] imqqurn g tmsgza n udanay d ar ifsser g tama n isaffn. Iga waylal ad yan ɣ imudar ittusmagln s ufuḍ s kigan, d ilkm uṭṭun n waylaln ad g taganin 420 hlli, d uṭṭun nnsn g tmqqilin ar ilkkem ar kra n 1500. Ikkattin ifsr g ku iẓẓlmḍ n tfriqt d [[Agmuḍ anammas|ugmmuḍ anammas]], d idrarn n Aleb d Uṛupa, waxxa yafuḍ g kra n 400 n usggʷas izrin.

Ar itturkan ufssr n udanay armiti agafan ɣilad g [[Agmuḍ anammas|ugmmuḍ anammas]] d [[Tafriqt n ugafa|iẓẓlmḍ n tfṛiqt]] d kra n tmnaḍin ɣ tiniri tamqqrant, slawann akkʷ g Umṛṛuk d [[Turkya|Tuṛkya]] d Ddzayr d [[Surya]]. Ar yadlli ittunna mas-d aylaln ad ar itturkan ufssr nnsn ɣar g [[Lmɣrib|Umṛṛuk]], ar kiɣ tettyufa yat tmsddurruyt g [[Surya]] g usggʷas n 2002. Adanay armiti illa ɣ [[Lmɣrib|Umṛṛuk]] g [[Asif n Massa|wasif n masst]].

